Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「赤龍帝的贈禮」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(424,436)}<Boostet Gear Gift>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉雅絲大人的「女王」一名 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(451,436)}<Queen>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱乃學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱乃學姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像損失了讓你引以自豪的左膀右臂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有佑斗和一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱乃學姐居然被打敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木場！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木場！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「擊破」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(424,436)}<Take>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉雅絲大人的「騎士」一名 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(453,436)}<Knight>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄遊戲（Resignation）吧 莉雅絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 只會傷害你那「主教」和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(566,436)}<Bishop>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所疼愛的「兵卒」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(473,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來晚了 尤貝露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如傳說一樣 那個「女王」確實厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(476,436)}<Queen>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是借助了它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏就是贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你就是最靠得住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那瓶子是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尼克斯的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼傷 都能讓其瞬間痊癒的 吾家一族的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這在遊戲裡是被准許的哦 最多可以使用兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們那也不是有擁有「聖母的微笑」的「主教」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(470,436)}<Twilight Healing>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(653,436)}<Bishop>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於我家一族才有能力製造這個 所以可以高價賣出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身加上眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從評估遊戲開始以來 菲尼克斯家就好事不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「升級」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19\pos(423,436)}<Promotion>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜予我「女王」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(439,436)}<Queen>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 我一定會讓社長贏得勝利的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 兵藤一誠 此刻參上！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小男孩「兵卒」和小姐「主教」就由我來對付…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(258,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(472,436)}<Bishop>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 還是我來把他們一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才能讓他們口服心服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些話 先打倒我再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放棄遊戲吧 莉雅絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經陷入困境了 我早就料到會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已被「將軍」了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴 萊薩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼入困境？預料？別說笑了 我這「王」還健在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(581,436)}<King>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我也無可奈何了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去實行那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛西亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那麼激烈的戰鬥 你竟然挺過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你約好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛西亞是我們的生命線 你先退一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛西亞！ 一誠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛西亞她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫髮無傷 她只是受刺激暈了過去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒想到他會用身體去抵擋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這樣一來「聖母的微笑」的力量就已經封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(383,436)}<Twilight Healing>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明從正面接受了我的攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「女王」的防禦力吧 你被「升級」得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(237,436)}<Queen>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19\pos(579,436)}<Promotion>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 這場比試還繼續的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是個笨蛋 所以不懂什麼是揭穿詭計和陷入困境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還可以戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我這個拳頭還能握得住就可以繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起打到萊薩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等 愛西亞 我們絕對會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Boost」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Boost」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一遍 「Boost」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Boost」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二遍 「Boost」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Burst」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「赤龍帝之籠手」所帶給寄宿的身體負荷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(272,436)}<Boostet Gear>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大到其他神器無法與之相比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說 強化力量這麼多次 還能繼續戰鬥這本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很接近奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力都落空了 還受到了尤貝露娜的直擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的負荷已經超過了肉體所能承受的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊薩！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉雅絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只剩下這點魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實地承認敗北 趕緊放棄遊戲如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不惜任何代價也要去贏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為最強的「兵卒」 我已經跟社長約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(391,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長還訓練了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個打不死的活屍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥 因為我是社長的「兵卒」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(611,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠 退下！ 快退下！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠 我什麼你不聽我的命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能讓社長笑出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡社長跟其他事沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為莉雅絲學姐對我來說是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很讓人不爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個僕人而已 硬是要跟我這萊薩‧菲尼克斯對抗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊薩 你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我只是順著他的意思 把他燒成灰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒到讓治療失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲中的死亡可以被當做事故來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你住手 萊薩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我輸了 我放棄遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「將軍」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認莉雅絲大人放棄遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場遊戲 萊薩‧菲尼克斯取得勝利
